updatefailureerror.message:
XIVLauncher mislyktes i å sjekke etter oppdateringer. Dette kan være forårsaket av tilkoblingsproblemer til GitHub. Vent noen minutter og prøv igjen.
Deaktiver VPN, hvis du har en. Du kan også måtte utelukke XIVLauncher fra antiviruset ditt.
Sjekk FAQ hvis problemet fortsetter etter flere minutter.

DalamudUnavailable.message: Programtillegg er ikke tilgjengelig på grunn av en spilloppdatering.

GamePathSafeguardError.message: Vennligst ikke velg "game" eller "boot" mappen til FFXIV-installasjonen, men velg heller mappen som inneholder disse i stedet.

GamePathInvalidError.message: Mappen du valgte har ingen FFXIV installasjon. XIVLauncher vil installere FFXIV første gangen du logger inn.

CheckLoginInfo.message: I tillegg, vennligst sjekk innloggingsinformasjonen din, eller prøv igjen.

MaintenanceQueueBootPatch.message:
Det ble oppdaget en ny oppdatering til FFXIV starteren.
Vanligvis betyr dette at det også finnes en oppdatering til spillet.

Du blir nå logget inn.

SettingsGamePatchPathError.message:
Game and patch download paths cannot be the same.
Please make sure to choose distinct game and patch download paths.

IntegrityCheckBase.message:
The game is not installed to the path you specified.
Please install the game before running an integrity check.

DalamudIncompatible.message:
Dalamud ble foreløpig ikke oppdatert til din nåværende FFXIV-versjon.
Detter vanlig etter patcher, så vennligst vær tålmodig eller spør på Discord etter en statusoppdatering.

DalamudCompatCheckFailed.message:
Kunne ikke kontakte tjeneren for å hente kompatible versjonen av Dalamud til gjeldende versjon av FFXIV. Dette kan bety at din .NET installasjon er for gammel.
Vennligst sjekk Discord for mer informasjon.

GameIsOpenPluginLocked.message: Spillet er åpent, vennligst lukk spillet og prøv igjen.

IntegrityCheckImpossible.message: Det er ingen referanserapport for denne spillversjonen ennå. Vennligst prøv igjen senere.

IntegrityCheckFailed.message:
Some game files seem to be modified or corrupted. 

If you use TexTools mods, this is an expected result.

If you do not use mods, right click the "Login" button on the XIVLauncher start page and choose "Repair game".

IntegrityCheckValid.message: Installasjonen av spillet ser ut til å være gyldig.

UpdateNotice.message: XIVLauncher has been updated to version {0}.

ChangelogLoadingError.message: Could not load changelog. Please check GitHub or Discord instead!

EmailInfo.message:
XIVLauncher is free, open-source software - it doesn't use any telemetry or analysis tools to collect your data, but it would help a lot if you could send me a short email with your operating system, why you use XIVLauncher and, if needed, any criticism or things we can do better. Your email will be deleted immediately after evaluation and I won't ever contact you.

Thank you very much for using XIVLauncher!

ChangelogThanks.message:
XIVLauncher is free, open-source software supported by a variety of people from all over the world.
Thank you for sticking around!

ChatChannelSetupDescription.message: Vennligst oppgi om XIVLauncher skal sende til en kanal i en server eller til en bruker via DM, og de respektive IDene.

ErrorExplanation.message:
An error in XIVLauncher occurred. Please consult the FAQ. If this issue persists, please report
it on GitHub by clicking the button below, describing the issue and copying the text in the box.

ChooseGamePathFTS.message:
Please select the folder your game is installed in.
It should contain the folders "game" and "boot".

FirstTimeSteamNotice.message: Kryss av i denne boksen om du vanligvis starter spillet med Steam.

ChooseDirectXFTS.message: Please select which DirectX version you want to use.

DirectX9NoticeFTS.message: DirectX 9 mode is not supported anymore. It will still start, but you will not get support from SE for any technical issues any additional XIVLauncher features such as Rich Presence and Dalamud will not work.

ChooseLanguageFTS.message: Please select which language you want to load the game with.

FirstTimeActLaunch.message:
Advanced Combat Tracker er installert på maskinen din.
Vil du starte det automatisk når spillet starter?

FirstTimeDalamudNotice.message:
Do you want to enable Dalamud?
This will add some extra functionality to your game, such as RMT chat filtering and Discord notifications for chat messages or Duty Finder pops.

To configure these settings, please use the XIVLauncher settings menu and switch to the "Dalamud" tab.
Enabling this, however, could cause a false positive in your antivirus software, please check its settings and add any needed exclusions if you run into problems.

GenericAddonSetupDescription.message: Vennligst velg programmet som skal startes, legg til eventuelle parametere og om det skal startes som administrator.

LoginWebExceptionContent.message:
XIVLauncher could not establish a connection to the game servers.

This may be a temporary issue, or a problem with your internet connection. Please try again later.

MaintenanceNotice.message: Maintenance seems to be in progress. The game shouldn't be launched.

LoginBoxLoginTooltip.message: Logg inn med de angitte opplysningene

LoginBoxWaitingForMaint.message: Venter på at vedlikeholdet skal bli ferdig...

AutoLoginIntro.message:
You are enabling Auto-Login.
This means that XIVLauncher will always log you in with the current account and you will not see this window.

To change settings and accounts, you have to hold the shift button on your keyboard while clicking the XIVLauncher icon.

GameIsOpenRepairError.message:
The game and/or the official launcher are open. XIVLauncher cannot repair the game if this is the case.
Please close them and try again.

GameRepairDisclaimer.message:
XIVLauncher will now try to find corrupted game files and repair them.
If you use any TexTools mods, this will replace all of them and restore the game to its initial state.

Do you want to continue?

CheckBootVersionError.message: XIVLauncher was not able to check the boot version for the select game installation. This can happen if a maintenance is currently in progress or if your connection to the version check server is not available. Please report this error if you are able to login with the official launcher, but not XIVLauncher.

GameIsOpenError.message:
Spillet og/eller det offisielle oppstartsprogrammet er åpent. XIVLauncher kan isåfall ikke oppdatere spillet.
Vennligst lukk det offisielle oppstartsprogrammet og prøv igjen.

PatcherAlreadyInProgress.message: XIVLauncher oppdaterer allerede spillet ditt i en annen forekomst. Vennligst sjekk om XIVLauncher ennå er åpen.

KillswitchText.message:
XIVLauncher cannot start the game at this time, as Square Enix has made changes to the login process.
We need to adjust to these changes and verify that our adjustments are safe before we can re-enable the launcher. Please try again later.

We apologize for these circumstances.

You can use the "Official Launcher" button below to start the official launcher.

SteamLinkingText.message: You may be prompted to link your Steam account to your Square Enix account.

EmailUsernameError.message: Please enter your SE account name, not your email address.

UidCacheInstallError.message:
You enabled the UID cache in the patcher settings.
This setting does not allow you to reinstall FFXIV.

If you want to reinstall FFXIV, please take care to disable it first.

LoginNoServiceMessage.message:
This Square Enix account cannot play FINAL FANTASY XIV.

If you bought FINAL FANTASY XIV on Steam, make sure to check the "Use Steam service account" checkbox while logging in.
If Auto-Login is enabled, hold shift while starting to access settings.

LoginAcceptTermsMessage.message: Please accept the FINAL FANTASY XIV Terms of Use in the official launcher.

EverythingIsFuckedMessage.message:
Certain essential game files were modified/broken by a third party and the game can neither update nor start.
You have to reinstall the completely game to continue.

If this keeps happening, please contact us via Discord.

PatchInstallDisclaimer.message:
A new patch has been found that needs to be installed before you can play.
Do you wish for XIVLauncher to install it?

LoginNoStartOk.message: An update check was executed and any pending updates were installed.

NativeLauncherError.message:
Could not start the game correctly. Please report this error.

HRESULT: 0x{0}

MultiboxDeniedWarning.message:
You can't launch more than two instances of the game by default.

Please check if there is an instance of the game that did not close correctly.

GameExitedPrematurelyError.message:
XIVLauncher could not detect that the game started correctly.

This may be a temporary issue. Please try restarting your PC. It is possible that your game installation is not valid.

BinaryNotPresentError.message:
Could not find the game executable.
This might be caused by your antivirus. You may have to reinstall the game.

GenericLoginError.message: Error occurred during login, please report this error.

LoginGenericServerIssue.message:
The server has sent an invalid response. This is known to occur during outages or when servers are under heavy load.
Please wait a minute and try again, or try using the official launcher.

You can learn more about outages on the Lodestone.

NoVersionReferenceError.message:
The version of the game you are on cannot be repaired by XIVLauncher yet, as reference information is not yet available.
Please try again later.

GameRepairSuccess.message:
Game files were verified by XIVLauncher. {0} {1} repaired.

Please log in normally.

GameRepairError.message:
An error occurred while repairing the game files.

You may have to reinstall the game.

OtpOneClickHint.message:
Or use the app!
Click here to learn more!

PatchEta.message: {0} igjen for å laste ned med fart på {1}/s.

ProfilePictureInputDescription.message: Vennligst skriv inn navn og verden til en karakter.

ChooseGamePath.message:
Vennligst velg mappen du har installert spillet i.
Den må inneholde mappene "game" og "boot".

OtpServerCheckBox.message: Enable XL Authenticator app/OTP macro support

ChooseDpiAwarenessHint.message: If game scaling appears wrong when using XIVLauncher, please attempt changing this setting.

ChooseDirectX.message: Vennligst velg hvilken DirectX versjon du vil bruke.

DirectX9Notice.message: DirectX 9 modus er ikke støttet lengere. Spillet vil starte, men du vil ikke få noe støtte fra Square Enix om det oppstår feil. Ytterlige funksjoner i XIVLauncher som støtte for Discord Rich Presence og spilltillegget vil ikke virke.

ChooseLanguage.message: Vennligst velg språket du vil starte spillet med.

ChooseLauncherLanguage.message: Please select the launcher language, requires a restart.

LauncherLanguageHelpCtaLoc.message: Notice any mistakes? You can help out translating the launcher! Just click here!

LauncherLanguageNotice.message: A restart is required to apply the launcher language setting.

AutoLaunchHint.message: Dette er programmene som starter så snart spillet har startet.

AutoLaunchAddNewToolTip.message: Legg til ny Autostart-oppføring som lar deg starte hvilket som helst program.

InGameAddonDescription.message:
These options affect the XIVLauncher in-game features, provided by Dalamud. These features will be automatically
enabled if you are running the DirectX 11 version of the game, the version of the game is
compatible, and the checkbox below is ticked.

InGameAddonCommandHint.message: Når aktivert, skriv "/xlhelp" i spillet for å se tilgjengelige kommandoer.

InGameAddonChatDelayDescription.message:
Se etter nylig sendte meldinger for å unngå duplikater.
Dette lar flere brukere bruke samme kanal som en pratelogg.
Vennligst angi en passende forsinkelse i millisekunder nedenfor (f.eks 1000).

InGameAddonInjectionDelayDescriptionLoc.message: Utsett injiseringen av tillegg i spillet. Dette lar deg gjemme de fra programmer som OBS og Discord, siden de vil injiseres før tilleggene.

InGameAddonLoadMethodEntryPointLoc.message: New: improves compatibility with certain other software and plugins that need to load early.

InGameAddonLoadMethodDllInjectLoc.message: Legacy: old version of the Dalamud injection system that may be more stable.

UniversalisHint.message: Data for markedstavle gitt i samarbeid med Universalis.

UniversalisOptOut.message: Avmeld meg fra å anonymt sende inn gruppeprodusert markedstavleinformasjon

PluginsDescriptionLoc.message: Dette er de tilgjengelige tilleggene som er installert på din maskin.

PluginsInstallHint.message: Du kan bruke /xlplugins kommandoen i spillet for å installere flere tillegg.

KeepPatches.message: Behold nedlastede oppdateringer for fremtidige ominstalleringer

PatchAcquisitionMethod.message: Choose the method used to acquire patches. We recommend "ARIA(HTTP)".

ResetUidCacheTip.message: Hold control while starting the launcher to reset the UID cache

LoginGenericError.message:
Could not log into your SE account.
Please check your username and password.

AdminCheck.message:
XIVLauncher og/eller FINAL FANTASY XIV kjører som administrator.
Dette kan forårsake forskjellige problemer, for eksempel kan det hende at tillegg ikke starter, og snarveistaster kan slutte å virke.

Vil du løse problemet automatisk?

AdminCheckNag.message:
XIVLauncher kjører som administrator.
Dette kan forårsake forskjellige problemer, for eksempel kan det hende at tillegg ikke starter, og snarveistaster kan slutte å virke.

Vennligst unngå å kjøre XIVLauncher som admin.

MacTypeNag.message:
MacType ble oppdaget på denne PCen.
Dette vil skape problemer med FFXIV; både med det offisielle oppstartsprogrammet og XIVLauncher.

Vennligst ekskluder XIVLauncher, ffxivboot, ffxivlauncher, ffxivupdater og ffxiv_dx11 fra MacType.

MyGamesWriteAccessNag.message:
You do not have permission to write to FFXIV's My Games folder.
This will prevent screenshots and some character data from being saved.

This may be caused by either your antivirus or a permissions error. Please check your My Games folder permissions.

GShadeError.message:
A broken GShade installation was detected.

The game cannot start. Do you want XIVLauncher to fix this? You will need to reinstall GShade.

PatchInstallerInstallFailed.message:
The patch installer ran into an error.
Please report this error.

Please try again or use the official launcher.

PatchInstallerNotOpen.message:
Kunne ikke koble til oppdateringsinstallatøren.
Vennligst rapporter denne feilen.

PatchManNoInstaller.message:
The patch installer could not start correctly.

If you have denied access to it, please try again. If this issue persists, please contact us via Discord.

DalamudRunnerError.message:
Could not launch Dalamud successfully. This might be caused by your antivirus.
To prevent this, please add an exception for the folder "%AppData%\XIVLauncher\addons".

AntivirusDeletedBoot.message:
The Dalamud boot DLL could not be found.

It was likely deleted by your antivirus software. Please add an exception for the XIVLauncher folder and try again.

DalamudVc2019RedistError.message: Tillegget til XIVLauncher i spillet krever de omdistruerbare Microsoft Visual C++ 2015-2019 pakkene for å fortsette. Vennligst installer dem fra Microsoft's hjemmeside.
